                                        <h2 id="job">Cognicor</h2>
                                            <p>Based out of Barcelona, CogniCor Technologies offers Cognitive Virtual Assistant exclusively for the banking and finance sector. Our coveted list of clients includes some of the biggest global names. Incorporated in the year 2013, the company is in a phase of fast growth, already having established physical footprints in three different continents.</p>
                                            <p>Artificial Intelligence market is growing worldwide. Businesses, cutting across industries and geographies, are investing heavily in cognitive and artificial intelligence-based business solutions. AI for long was touted as the next big thing but it was only the recent advances that have kicked in a commercialization drive. These advances were largely brought about by explorations made by many into the very nature of intelligence. It is a curiosity to understand the intelligent life that has led to the formation of the company. </p>
                                            <p>The transformative potential that AI holds is slowly coming to fruition. We pride ourselves on being a part of this global drive to engineer the future. We would be glad if you could join us and support us by granting access to your talent pool. The journey would be exciting for the students as well. Because like AI technologies, they would be constantly expanding their limits and evolving into better engineers and moreover better human beings</p>
                                            <p><strong>Post: NLP/ML engineers</strong></p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Mode of Exam: Online</li>
                                                <li>Further process: At their own campus at Infopark</li>
